{"tid":1156893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[發大財] 紅隧三車相撞11傷　中港牌私家車司機涉醉駕","createTime":"2019-05-16T01:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T01:53:50.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e7699c7c33e952233421aafb1839249023d7434f","tid":1156893,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"紅隧三車相撞11傷 中港牌私家車司機涉醉駕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190516/s00001/1557969405199/%E7%B4%85%E9%9A%A7%E4%B8%89%E8%BB%8A%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E11%E5%82%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%8C%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%B6%89%E9%86%89%E9%A7%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190516%2Fs00001%2F1557969405199%2F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E9%259A%25A7%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2592%259E11%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%258C%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2586%2589%25E9%25A7%2595&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2K0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=da553a2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190516%2Fs00001%2F1557969405199%2F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E9%259A%25A7%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2592%259E11%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%258C%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2586%2589%25E9%25A7%2595&h=5dd61039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190516/s00001/1557969405199/%E7%B4%85%E9%9A%A7%E4%B8%89%E8%BB%8A%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E11%E5%82%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%8C%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%B6%89%E9%86%89%E9%A7%95</a><br />\n<br />\n紅磡海底隧道凌晨實施單管雙程行車期間，發生三車相撞意外，釀成11人傷，一名私家車司機涉酒後駕駛被捕。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨4時06分，一輛掛有中港車牌的賓利私家車，沿紅隧往香港方向行駛時，疑爬頭越線，迎頭直撼鄰線一輛往九龍方向行駛的N11線城巴，私家車車尾撞向尾隨一輛的士。三車車頭嚴重損毀，其中城巴車頭擋風玻璃碎裂，車上有組件飛脫，散落一地。<br />\n<br />\n三車司機、城巴上4男3女乘客及的士上一名男乘客受輕傷，清醒送伊利沙伯醫院治理。50歲私家車司機的酒精呼氣測試結果達55度，超標逾一倍，警方以涉嫌酒後駕駛拘捕司機。"},{"pid":"b0b5fea5d4172e8e154981cad16eb4e3e761c9db","tid":1156893,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:52:15.000Z","msg":"醉駕判終身啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c930d1dd13713870e24651ea66278e7c72717510","tid":1156893,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:53:50.000Z","msg":"賓利當坦克咁渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}